  "comment": "2x 110W LED Stage Blinder - Warm White with Amber Drift\nIntroducing the B BLINDED, the ultimate solution for all your blinder needs!\nWith the 2x 110W warm white LED engine and tungsten emulation feature, the B BLINDED produces an output comparable to DWE 2x 650X, but with many extra functionalities. Say goodbye to dimmers and cables, and enjoy the faster installation and more creativity with this powerful fixture. The B BLINDED is also highly versatile and allows you to create a 4, 6, and even 8-lite blinder unit up to a 20-lite, either vertically or horizontally. This all-weather fixture is extremely bright and features a strobe function with a refresh rate of 1200Hz, making it perfect for any stage.",
